These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, tea
There are 2 different favourite colors: emerald, aquamarine
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: punk, funk
2 different games are played: canasta, bridge
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: iris, dahlia
The people use 2 different means of transport: subway, tram
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: june, november
1. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the person who likes aquamarine##3
2. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
3. the fan of funk is on the left of the fan of punk##1
4. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
5. the person who's birthday is in november is the fan of funk##1
6. the person playing bridge is the person who likes emerald##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |
| Beverage      | tea        | hot-chocolate |
| Color          | aquamarine  | emerald     |
| Music-Genre         | funk    | punk         |
| Game           | canasta    | bridge |
| Flower   | iris  | dahlia     |
| Transport           | tram      | subway    |
| Birthday         | november | june          |

