.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-3-2::.
There 2 different types of food: garlic, lime
House: wooden, victorian
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: february, january
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, tiparillo
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, milk
2 different pets are kept: goat, mouse
City: miami, nizza
1. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person eating garlic##1
2. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the victorian house##1
3. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
4. the owner of the goat is on the left or right of the person eating garlic##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2       |
| Food         | garlic      | lime       |
| House           | wooden | victorian |
| Birthday   | january      | february        |
| Cigar   | old-henry         | tiparillo        |
| Beverage   | almond-milk    | milk       |
| Pet           | mouse        | goat          |
| City     | nizza          | miami    |

